> @@ -0,0 +1,326 @@
> +/*
> + * QEMU CBOR helpers
> + *
> + * Copyright (c) 2024 Dorjoy Chowdhury <dorjoychy111@gmail.com>
> + *
> + * This work is licensed under the terms of the GNU GPL, version 2 or
> + * (at your option) any later version.  See the COPYING file in the
> + * top-level directory.
